Text: RE Your presentation Cc Im very happy you found the presentation useful Im working very closely with Adam Kulick who you probably know Please let me know if you have any questions or if you have any difficulty opening the file Best regards Alla Original Message From Vince J Kaminski mailto Sent Monday June PM To Gil Alla Cc Vince J Kaminski Subject Your presentation Alla I enjoyed your presentation at Risk last week I would appreciate an electronic copy of the documentation Vince Kaminski Vincent Kaminski Managing Director Research Enron Corp Smith Street Room EB Houston TX Phone Fax Email RiskCongressppt
